name: Mandorak Beach
description:
The most common activity to do in Mandorak Beach is definitely sunset watching. The fact is that the beach features a distinct sunset view, which looks more romantic than others. Tourists need to come at the right time to enjoy the sunset. At least, they must have been there before dusk and carry chosen the right spot to witness such an amazing view of nature.
Mandorak Beach is famous for its crystal clear water. The weak waves and amazing visibility of the sea make it perfect for water sports like swimming and snorkeling, therefore.
